OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStill a few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, wintry on high
OL,7,Fground, becoming more isolated then
OL,8,Fdying out overnight as skies become
OL,9,Fclear. Winds falling light with a
OL,10,Ffrost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunshine, the best in the
OL,14,Fmorning with some high cloud arriving
OL,15,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,16,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
